{"tid":855797,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【施政報告】湯家驊大讚報告劃時代：一反歷屆政府小修小補心態","createTime":"2018-10-10T09:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T08:29:17.000Z","uid":196678,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5d24e95b7d471e33f240f8cf0387221e3dfcfd","tid":855797,"uid":196678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥今早11點將在立法會宣讀任內第二份施政報告，身兼行政會議成員的民主思路召集人湯家驊今早在facebook留言，形容今次是一份歷史性的施政報告，「一反過往回歸之來歷屆政府那種以左顧右盼、小修小補之心態」。<br />\n湯落力讚揚新一份施政報告具理念性，「充滿管治信心、彰顯共同希望的報告」，又指「與過往歷屆特首不同，這是一份從現屆政府的管治理念出發，在各項具爭議性課題作出決定性處理政策的報告」，他透露，報告刻劃了香港未來2、30年的宏觀發展藍圖，但又補充指社會不應期望一份施政報告可解決所有深層次和特別的政治問題。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181010/58776691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58776691&d=asgtric5%2Fy7YLeUHCcb7WgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=8636520d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58776691&h=8ec0cd7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181010/58776691</a>"},{"pid":"48a0718e02c0f56e213ae59c02c22d478a2d16b0","tid":855797,"uid":26329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:23:44.000Z","msg":"劃時代垃圾"},{"pid":"b864d79bcdba7f074a2264322a71c234746f4747","tid":855797,"uid":12441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"雪廠街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e590d896b561fa1b780419dee40b36efe2ee0ecd","tid":855797,"uid":59976,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/eqiao/1325940847-3089128426.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Feqiao%2F1325940847-3089128426.jpg&h=3733f1cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdc6c6a334caa7ad5029dae